      <p class="section-subtitle">From conversation to crisis prevention in under 3 minutes</p>

      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3 class="step-title">Senior Speaks Naturally</h3>
            <p class="step-text">Voice-first interface with 3-second pause tolerance, hearing aid compatibility, and medical vocabulary</p>
            <details class="step-disclosure">
              <summary class="disclosure-trigger">Technical Details</summary>
              <div class="disclosure-content">
                <p>• Whisper STT + Piper TTS = $0 API costs</p>
                <p>• 95%+ accuracy for senior voices</p>
                <p>• Background noise filtering</p>
              </div>
            </details>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3 class="step-title">AI Analyzes & Responds</h3>
            <p class="step-text">7 therapeutic agents provide clinical-grade support with 98.7% crisis detection accuracy</p>
